snippet.title: Minecraft on PS1 - "Fromage" PlayStation Homebrew
snippet.description:
Fromage is a sandbox game engine for the PS1 inspired by the classic 2009 release of Minecraft
(Quote from https://chenthread.asie.pl/fromage/ )
Created by: asie, GreaseMonkey

💾 Info & Download: https://chenthread.asie.pl/fromage/

📑 Index 📑

0:00 Loading
0:36 Bulding (Music by GreaseMonkey)
3:45 Testing "Extreme" distance
4:13 TNT, Water, Lava, Sponge
5:57 Flat world, Save & Load
7:25 Blocks showcase
8:00 "Quake pro" testing
8:18 Credits
